Package edu.handong.csee.java.chatcounter

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChatCounter
    This class is controller class ChatCounter
    FileLoader
    This class lists all the files into the array then extracts the messages from each file into two separate ArrayList one for CSV and one for TXT
    FileWriter
    This class Writes all produces the final output of the program, ChatCounter
    MessageParser
    This class parses each messages from txt file and csv file into the format that i want it to be Used regular expression to extract time name and message and concatenated the lines once again in the same format so Redundancy check will be alot easier
    PMCounter
    This class counts the number of chat made by each person in class and returns them in HashMap which is convenient to express a String with a corresponding integer
    RedundancyChecker
    This class checks if any redundant messages are made in the chat if the user made the exact same message at the exact time then the two corresponding messages are merged to one
